  "sketchCode": "// Lesson 1 — Blink\n// Turn an LED on pin 13 on and off every half second.\n\nvoid setup() {\n  pinMode(13, OUTPUT);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  digitalWrite(13, HIGH);\n  delay(500);\n  digitalWrite(13, LOW);\n  delay(500);\n}\n",
